</span></h2><p class="sc-hjGZqJ fRpwCv pf-41_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-43_"><b>What it is</b> - Recognising and understanding one's emotions, strengths, weaknesses, and triggers.<br><b>Why it matters</b> - We can only set genuine goals and make authentic changes by knowing ourselves.<br>

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-44_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-46_"><b>Self-regulation</b>


</span></h3><p class="sc-hjGZqJ fRpwCv pf-47_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-49_"><b>What it is</b> - Managing and controlling our emotional responses and reactions to various situations.<br><b>Why it matters</b> - It aids in decision-making, helps maintain a positive environment, and ensures momentary impulses do not rule us.
<br>


</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-50_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-52_"><b>Motivation</b>


</span></h3><p class="sc-hjGZqJ fRpwCv pf-53_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-55_"><b>What it is</b> - The inner drive that fuels our actionsâ€”beyond external rewards.<br><b>Why it matters</b> - Intrinsic motivation sustains our momentum even when external motivators (like money or praise) are absent.
<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-56_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-58_"><b>Personal responsibility
</b>


</span></h3><p class="sc-hjGZqJ fRpwCv pf-59_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-61_"><b>What it is</b> - Owning up to one's actions, decisions, successes, and failures.<br>

<b>Why it matters</b> - It fosters trust, credibility, and, most importantly, growth from experiences.
<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-62_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-64_">Harnessing the power of self-leadership: Practical steps

</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Harnessing_the_power_of_self-leadership_Practical_steps_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.png?v=1695374373" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Harnessing_the_power_of_self-leadership_Practical_steps_-_Dr_Richard_Dune.png?v=1695374373 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Harnessing_the_power_of_self-leadership_Practical_steps_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_500x.png?v=1695374373 320w" width="1301" height="867" alt="Harnessing the power of self-leadership: Practical steps - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Harnessing the power of self-leadership: Practical steps - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-uojGG kTBJzQ pf-65_"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-66_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-68_"><b>Start with reflection

</b>


</span></h3><p class="sc-hjGZqJ fRpwCv pf-69_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-71_">Begin by setting aside time daily or weekly to reflect. Understand what's working in your life and what's not. Journaling can be a powerful tool here.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-72_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-74_"><b>Set clear, achievable goals


</b>


</span></h3><p class="sc-hjGZqJ fRpwCv pf-75_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-77_">Once you've reflected, know where you want to go. Have a clear vision, whether it's a personal aspiration or a professional milestone.

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-78_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-80_"><b>Stay accountable



